Invocation Name: super hero quiz
des:
This quiz contains over fifty questions related to superhero characters from Marvel and DC. You will hear a question and if your device has a screen, you will see an image associated with the question. You will be able to ask to repeat the question, get the answer, move on to the next question. You can stop the quiz at any time by saying stop.
The questions relate to characters such as:
- Superman
- Spiderman
- Batman
- Silver Surfer
- Rom
etc
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
